62
00:11:00,620 --> 00:11:02,010
Do you remember what it was?

63
00:11:05,830 --> 00:11:07,970
Don't make trouble for you.

64
00:11:08,770 --> 00:11:10,620
Since you still keep it in mind,

65
00:11:11,170 --> 00:11:13,140
why did you not discipline your son

66
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:15,530
and made a scene to expel the teacher?

67
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,550
Now, the whole board

68
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:19,100
thought it was my idea.

69
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:23,550
They say the Zhang family throws our weight around

70
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:25,190
and bullies a female teacher.

71
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:28,380
