226
00:23:26,570 --> 00:23:27,960
You said a few days?

227
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:30,860
I'll miss you so much.

228
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:33,250
Tell me

229
00:23:34,050 --> 00:23:35,140
