230
00:23:39,510 --> 00:23:40,520
Hey.

231
00:23:43,120 --> 00:23:44,090
Okay.

232
00:23:44,510 --> 00:23:45,510
I'll miss you, too.

233
00:23:51,480 --> 00:23:53,330
All right, then.

