00:24:54,180 --> 00:24:56,280
In order to win a scholarship, Xia Yuxin

255
00:24:56,070 --> 00:24:58,850
[Certificate of Merit]

256
00:24:56,580 --> 00:24:58,970
works hard every day to get first place.

257
00:25:00,360 --> 00:25:02,080
If I were her,

258
00:25:02,080 --> 00:25:04,050
I would take my mom's money, too.

259
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:07,040
I never thought she's so pitiful.

260
00:25:08,590 --> 00:25:10,270
