268
00:25:25,260 --> 00:25:26,820
And none of you can let my mom know

269
00:25:26,820 --> 00:25:27,450
that I know.

270
00:25:28,330 --> 00:25:29,840
So Xia Yuxin will still be paid by my mom.

271
00:25:31,520 --> 00:25:32,820
You want her to tattle on you

272
00:25:32,820 --> 00:25:34,130
to the chairwoman?

273
00:25:34,760 --> 00:25:36,520
Of course we have to get her on board first.

274
00:25:37,060 --> 00:25:39,330
Then, give her a little something to get by now and then.

275
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,600
Every once in a while, we go big.

276
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:43,450
In this way,

277
00:25:43,450 --> 00:25:44,330
my mom would think

278
00:25:44,330 --> 00:25:46,180
everything is under her control,

279
00:25:46,510 --> 00:25:47,860
and we won't be busted.

280
00:25:48,360 --> 00:25:50,210
Senior, you want to abuse your mom's money?

281
00:25:51,970 --> 00:25:52,810
I'm in.

282
00:25:53,950 --> 00:25:54,910
I'm in.

